This extension's chat webview (`webviews/chat-react/`) adapts code from:

  Continue (continuedev/continue)
  https://github.com/continuedev/continue
  Licensed under Apache License, Version 2.0

The Apache License 2.0 requires that we (a) retain copyright notices in
adapted files, (b) list the ported files here, and (c) note that the
adapted sources have been modified.

Each adapted source file begins with a 5-line header:

    // Adapted from continuedev/continue (Apache 2.0).
    // Source: <original path in continuedev/continue>
    // Commit: <SHA>
    // Modifications: <summary>

Files adapted in Sprint 068 (v0.15.0):

  webviews/chat-react/src/theme/VscThemeProvider.tsx
    ← gui/src/context/VscTheme.tsx (partial — propagates theme kind,
      drops TextMate token colour extraction)

  webviews/chat-react/src/hooks/useWebviewListener.ts
    ← gui/src/hooks/useWebviewListener.ts (narrowed to our HostToWebview
      union; otherwise structurally equivalent)

Additional files will be added here as Phase 2 ports the TipTap editor,
